import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.abs(x1)
    v1 = jnp.subtract(v0, x0)
    v2 = jnp.tanh(v0)
    v3 = jnp.abs(v1)
    v4 = jnp.add(x0, v3)
    v5 = jnp.subtract(v0, v4)
    v6 = jnp.abs(x0)
    v7 = jnp.minimum(v5, v5)
    v8 = jnp.minimum(v7, x0)
    return v8
